column5: Anyone have any ice depth reports for the areas around Fox and Snake Islands? Itching for a Whitey outing......  Any info would be appreciated.  Meely
I'm itching too Meely!!  I might go for the walk on wed or thursday this week. I'll let ya know what I see out there!!  Sinker
I heard some guys tried to walk out to fox and had to turn around  I would wait a few more days
